<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.9.10">
<l>āycciyaṉ ṟāḻip pirāṉpuṟam pulkiya</l>
<l>vēyttaṭan tōḷicol viṭṭucit taṉmakiḻn</l>
<l>tītta tamiḻivai yīraintum vallavar</l>
<l>vāyttanaṉ makkaḷaip peṟṟu makiḻvarē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who master these ten tamiḻ [verses] that joyously grant</l>
<l>the words of the wide-bamboo-shouldered lady,</l>
<l>the cowherdess who was embraced by the discus Lord from behind that day</l>
<l>by Viṭṭucittaṉ, begetting good children who flourish, they will rejoice.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
